import React from 'react'
import { Fragment } from 'react'
import { Card, CardGroup } from 'react-bootstrap'

function ProductCard(prouucts) {
    return (
        <Fragment >
          <CardGroup className="col-lg-3 m-1" key={prouucts.id}>
                <Card>
                    <Card.Body className="text-light bg-dark">
                        <Card.Img src={prouucts.image} alt="user" />
                        <Card.Title className="text-success">{prouducts.title}</Card.Title>
                        <Card.Text>
                          
                        </Card.Text>
                    </Card.Body>
                </Card>
            </CardGroup>
           
        </Fragment>
    )
}

export default ProductCard
